data.description: Better than new home awaits you! Spacious and light-filled 2-story modern home has so many upgrades!  With energy-efficient solar panels, on-demand water, and fiber optic ethernet routed throughout the house, this home is designed to be both environmentally friendly and technologically advanced. Automatic blinds with remote, phone app and timer, add convenience and enhance your privacy.  This home offers the perfect blend of indoor /outdoor living, with open layout connecting kitchen, dining, and great room to the extended deck, making it an ideal space for entertaining guests or simply relaxing with loved ones.  The unfinished walkout basement and large deck overlooking the east end of Windsor Reservoir provide an excellent opportunity to create a personalized living space. The backyard is xeriscaped, hot tub ready and is waiting for you to make it your own. Enjoy modern amenities with the kitchen's upgraded features: double electric ovens, gas cook top, large quartz island, numerous soft-close drawers and cabinets.  A large walk-in pantry will accommodate your kitchen storage needs. The two flex rooms (upper and main floors) provide versatility to suit your unique needs, whether you need dedicated home offices, playrooms, or creative spaces. Primary bath and upper floor second bathroom are both equipped with Bluetooth speakers/ fans (adjust with remote or your phone app), allowing you to listen to your favorite tunes or podcasts while relaxing. Automatic irrigation system in the front yard lets you set it and forget it, while non-potable water from the metro district keeps your water bill low.  Walk to Severance Shores Park and Windsor Reservoir walking trail.  Don't miss the chance to make this move-in ready gem your dream home! Buyer to verify all information. Part of a Metro District.  Assumable VA Loan.
